{
  "id": "61e91b3cb3495c001e9ef9c5",
  "title": "(5.3.1.1) Skip nameplate making",
  "created": 1556180212,
  "updated": 1556180212,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "61e91b3caff09e0000d0b36d",
      "text": "(5.3.1.1) Skip nameplate making",
      "created": 1556180212,
      "updated": 1556180212,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3caff09e0000d0b36e",
      "text": "Sometimes, I skip the \"[nameplate making]\" phase. It is a method to ease the burden of too much information. ",
      "created": 1556180212,
      "updated": 1556180212,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3caff09e0000d0b36f",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1556180212,
      "updated": 1556180212,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3caff09e0000d0b370",
      "text": "Jiro Kawakita proposed to repeat the nameplate making and further grouping until the pieces became several groups. Since making a nameplate is useful for understanding what good group organization is, it is important to experience it several times.",
      "created": 1556180212,
      "updated": 1556180212,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3caff09e0000d0b371",
      "text": "However, once you understand what a good group organization is, I think you can skip it in your daily work.",
      "created": 1556180212,
      "updated": 1556180212,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3caff09e0000d0b372",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1556180212,
      "updated": 1556180212,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3caff09e0000d0b373",
      "text": "In my case, I made nameplates when I made the table of contents from 600 pieces of paper. ",
      "created": 1556180212,
      "updated": 1556180212,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3caff09e0000d0b374",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1556180212,
      "updated": 1556180212,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3caff09e0000d0b375",
      "text": "After that, by dividing it into chapters, the number of pieces become 60 to 100 pieces. I did not make nameplates for those. I skip the phase and go \"[spatial arrangement]\" phase directly.",
      "created": 1556180212,
      "updated": 1556180212,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3caff09e0000d0b376",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1556180212,
      "updated": 1556180212,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3caff09e0000d0b377",
      "text": "Of course, if I come up with something new during the process, I write it to prevent it disappears.",
      "created": 1556180212,
      "updated": 1556180212,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "61e91b3caff09e0000d0b378",
      "text": "[en.icon]",
      "created": 1556180212,
      "updated": 1556180212,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    }
  ]
}